cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.SE, cs.CY, cs.HC

This paper deals with the privacy concerns related to advertising libraries on Android, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The study involves analyzing the interface between ad libraries and their host applications, which could also be categorized under software engineering (cs.SE) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of APIs to leak private information also involves the study of system integration (cs.SI) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY).
